body.description: Vitafusion Adult Gummy Vitamins for Men are daily vitamins formulated to address the health needs of men(1). Each two-gummy serving combines essential vitamins and minerals with natural fruit flavors to provide a delicious alternative to hard-to-swallow vitamin pills. Each serving provides immune system, muscle and energy metabolism support (1) and is an excellent source of Vitamin A, Vitamin C and Vitamin D. This daily multivitamin also contains Vitamins E, B6 and B12, along with Biotin, Zinc, Iodine and Folic Acid. These daily multivitamins for men contain no high-fructose corn syrup, artificial sweeteners, gluten, dairy or synthetic dyes. This 150-count bottle of vitamin gummies has enough for 75 days. Vitafusion Adult Gummy Multivitamins for Men were the recipient of the 2021 ChefsBest Excellence Award (2). Take a fruitful step toward a healthier, happier world with America’s Number-1 Gummy Vitamin Brand. (1) These statements have not been evaluated by the Food and Drug Administration. This product is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure or prevent any disease. (2) The ChefsBest Excellence Award is awarded to brands that surpass quality standards established by independent professional chefs. Evaluation funded by Church & Dwight Co., Inc.
